<L>Union supreme of wisdom, love, and power!</L>
<L>Pain'd, shrivill'd, gasping, from the forceful ray</L>
<L>How crept my mite Philosophers away?</L>
<L><PB N="15" REF="021065_0014_0FB2398F0BA99880">
In vain my Methodist, brave Herbert, cried,</L>
<L>And whin'd, and wrote, pretended, pray'd, and lied <NOTE N="*" PLACE="foot">See Lord Cherburg's Cock-Lane-Ghost Tale of Thunder's answer to Prayer.
 SCRIBLERUS.</NOTE>,</L>
