<L><PB N="17" REF="021065_0016_0FB23992CB796890">
I seized the work myself, Straight, in a cloud</L>
<L>Of night involv'd, to Scotia's <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 word"> rode.</L>
