<L>And thus the sage, and thus his teacher, <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 word"></L>
<L>All things roll on, by fix'd eternal <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 word"></L>
<L>Yet no effect depends upon a <GAP DESC="illegible" REASON="indecipherable" EXTENT="1 span"></L>
